channel.title: My Compiler...?
channel.description:
Hey everyone, I recently came back into private servers.. I used to own a server, but then I got a huge virus. And it wiped out everything... I'm Just wondering how do you work the compiler, because whenever i use mod taharok's... it gives me this
[code] You do not have JDK 5.0 or 6.0. We suggest u Download it! Press any key to continue... [/code]
Well I have downloaded it, now I don't know what to do... :\ Thanks for looking/helping!
~Sebo
